{"id":173460,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/南周程焕文-精神圣地——陈寅恪故居修复开放（/","date":"2011-08-21T21:02:59Z","modified":"2011-08-21T21:02:59Z","title":"南周程焕文 | 精神圣地——陈寅恪故居修复开放（组图）","content":"<p><p>11月12日）是中山大学85周年校庆日（孙中山先生的诞辰纪念日）。作为中山大学85周年校庆的最重要活动，中山大学的学术精神圣地——陈寅恪故居修缮开放仪式于上午10时在陈寅恪故居北草坪隆重举行，中山大学党委书记郑德涛教授、校长黄达人教授、常务副书记梁庆寅教授、副校长陈春声教授、陈寅恪先生的大女儿陈流求与三女儿陈美延及其家属、海内外嘉宾、中大师生等参加了开放仪式。现发照片若干以飨网友。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>一、陈寅恪故居外景</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829091f889a&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829091f889a&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782909f089a6&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782909f089a6&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78290a8a3c19&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78290a8a3c19&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78290b41b18c&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78290b41b18c&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78290be63c9a&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78290be63c9a&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78290c576d26&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78290c576d26&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78290cad69b3&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78290cad69b3&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>二、陈寅恪故居修复开放仪式</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static9.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78290d268338&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static9.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78290d268338&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>由于北方冷空气的南下，今日上午广州一直下着大雨，校办主任陈望南（打雨伞者）冒雨指挥场景布置。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78290e973e2e&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78290e973e2e&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>上午10时大雨骤然停止，天开一窗，持续约30分钟，老天爷仿佛特别关照中山大学，专为陈寅恪故居修复开放仪式停止降雨。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static9.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78291055e6c8&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static9.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78291055e6c8&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>校党委书记郑德涛教授的致辞被各路记者认为是有史以来最好的同类致辞。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782910e05507&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782910e05507&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829119d21c2&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829119d21c2&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>陈寅恪先生的长女陈流求老师（80岁）深情回顾父亲在中大的岁月，感谢中大历任领导对陈寅恪先生和家人的关心与照顾，特别感谢陈寅恪先生的助手黄萱和周连宽（世人多不知道周连宽的重大贡献），以及图书馆的刘少雄先生（86岁），并向图书馆赠送陈寅恪先生的著作。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782912200be7&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782912200be7&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>郑德涛书记、黄达人校长、陈寅恪先生的女儿陈流求、陈美延为陈寅恪故居修复开放揭匾</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782912874e82&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782912874e82&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>三、陈寅恪故居一楼大堂内景</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829155f2e23&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829155f2e23&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782916081503&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782916081503&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829177a07bc&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829177a07bc&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>左壁为容商弟子陈炜湛教授题写的陈寅恪先生名句：“士之读书治学，盖将以脱心志于俗谛之桎梏，真理因得以发扬。”</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782a30003169&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782a30003169&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> 右壁为陈寅恪故居简介</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static12.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829198c598b&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static12.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829198c598b&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>正中为陈寅恪先生铜像</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>四、陈寅恪故居客厅</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782a1c89b722&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782a1c89b722&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>大门右侧是通向陈寅恪先生“故居”的楼梯（陈寅恪先生曾长期居住在本楼二楼）</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78291e1237a5&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78291e1237a5&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>二楼客厅悬挂着饶宗颐先生的题字</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78291ef9d327&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78291ef9d327&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>对面是陈寅恪先生画像</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782920e22614&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782920e22614&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>在客厅入口处的墙边树立的是陈寅恪先生当年最好的书架，内为陈寅恪先生当年使用的线装书。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782921a90ade&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782921a90ade&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>客厅内摆放着陈寅恪先生当年常坐的藤椅。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78292237d219&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78292237d219&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>五、陈寅恪先生的起居室</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782922c508bf&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782922c508bf&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782923849c51&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782923849c51&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782924356d0c&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782924356d0c&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>五屉柜为陈寅恪先生当年使用的原物</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782924dd3911&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782924dd3911&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829258f370f&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829258f370f&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>在陈寅恪先生的夫人唐筼的书桌旁摆放着陈寅恪当年使用的藤椅，陈寅恪先生当年经常在此收听收音机广播。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78292b10e0d7&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78292b10e0d7&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78292b908eea&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78292b908eea&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>陈寅恪先生当年使用的铺盖非常普通。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78292c18ec01&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78292c18ec01&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>起居室外的走廊是书房</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78292cdca67f&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78292cdca67f&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>六、陈寅恪先生的书房</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78292d7b5bd5&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78292d7b5bd5&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>这里是陈寅恪先生的书房，也是陈寅恪先生的助手黄萱等人的工作场所。书房内摆放的全是陈寅恪先生当年使用的书籍</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78292de77272&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static3.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78292de77272&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>桌面上摆放着一把手摇铜铃（非原物）。当年陈寅恪先生在走廊上课时，助手有时会用手摇铜铃提醒下课时间。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78292e5c7333&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static4.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78292e5c7333&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782a242f72dd&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782a242f72dd&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>七、陈寅恪先生的教室</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782934dae8d9&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782934dae8d9&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>陈寅恪先生当年在此走廊上课，墙壁上挂有两块黑板，一块大的供教学使用，一块小的供自己使用。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>八、陈寅恪先生女儿们的居室</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static1.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782935acf710&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static1.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782935acf710&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>因为布展的需要，陈寅恪先生女儿的居室现在用于专门陈列陈寅恪先生的著作、手稿等珍贵文献。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829365e1c81&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static2.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829365e1c81&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782936dd796c&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782936dd796c&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78293748f91e&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78293748f91e&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>九、一楼右侧北厢房</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782937e75d49&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782937e75d49&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>东南区一号在陈寅恪先生居住时和居住前后曾经居住过不少著名大家，包括谢志光、周寿恺、黄萱、王起、杨荣国、容庚、商承祚等等。此室悬挂着这些著名教授的照片和简要学术成就介绍，同时陈列着其主要著作。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782938bf4a84&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782938bf4a84&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78293930ca6e&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static15.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78293930ca6e&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static1.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78293ca5c2c0&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static1.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78293ca5c2c0&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>十、一楼右侧南厢房</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782a29a05b85&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782a29a05b85&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static9.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78293e8b6d68&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static9.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78293e8b6d68&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>大致模仿当年各位教授在此居住的场景，古香古色。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78293f56b23d&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78293f56b23d&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg78293fceaf79&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg78293fceaf79&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>十一、一楼客厅</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782940787f29&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static10.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782940787f29&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>一楼客厅的四壁悬挂着季羡林、饶宗颐、唐长儒、刘大年等大家为纪念陈寅恪先生的题词。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782940d577a4&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static5.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782940d577a4&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>十二、一楼南面内走廊</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782941681f6d&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782941681f6d&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829445eb275&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829445eb275&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782945f54b8f&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782945f54b8f&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg7829466376fd&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg7829466376fd&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=4978019f0100fip6&#038;url=http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/4978019fg782946faa206&#038;690\"><img src=\"http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/4978019fg782946faa206&#038;690\" /></a></p>\n<p>汪荣祖教授（左）、陈流求（中）、陈美延（右）在走廊留影</p>\n<p>敬请阅读：中山大学新闻：<span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news2.sysu.edu.cn/ShowArticle.aspx?ArticleID=8230\"><span>陈寅恪故居昨日修复开放</span></a>（组图）</span></p>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/08/c3faaf53829091f889a690-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":699,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}